WEBVTT

00:00.101 --> 00:02.254
<i>Previously on Mad Men...</i>

00:04.113 --> 00:05.458
<i>You're going to
have a love scene.</i>

00:05.570 --> 00:07.561
And between you, me and
soon a national audience,

00:07.755 --> 00:09.359
it's more of a love affair.

00:09.969 --> 00:11.446
Oh, my goodness.

00:11.603 --> 00:13.092
I don't want to live on
the Upper East Side.

00:13.204 --> 00:14.082
Why?

00:14.181 --> 00:17.298
I saw us raising our kids in a place
with more different kinds of people.

00:18.394 --> 00:20.944
We created a human life.

00:22.111 --> 00:23.498
When you told me
about the merger,

00:23.648 --> 00:25.667
I hoped he would
rub off on you.

00:25.776 --> 00:27.667
Obviously, you're on his side.

00:27.817 --> 00:29.954
Why did you do it all
off their sides?

