46:44.824 --> 46:48.259
<i>♪ Always something there</i>
<i>to remind me ♪</i>

46:50.329 --> 46:54.832
<i>♪ I was born to love you ♪</i>

46:54.866 --> 46:57.868
<i>♪ And I will never be free ♪</i>

46:57.902 --> 47:01.171
<i>♪ You'll always be</i>
<i>a part of me ♪</i>

